fields.title: Create Accont
fields.text:
Create Account

  • First Name: Given name.
  • Last Name: Family name.
  • Email: Personal or organization email address.
  • Organization: The university or organization that your are affiliated with.
  • Password: Eight character, uncommon, alpha-numeric password.

fields.title: Login
fields.text:
Login

  • Email address: The email address you created your account with.
  • Password: The alpha-numeric password you chose.
  • Lost Password: If you cannot remember your password you can reset it here.

fields.title: Reset Password
fields.text:
Rest Password

  • Email Address: The address you are using to access this system. A link will be sent to this address to reset your account. You must be able to access the specified email account. If your email address needs to be changed and you cannot log in, please contact us for a resolution.

fields.title: Experiments
fields.text:
Experiments

  • Name: Title of the experiments.
  • Link: URL to access the experiment.

fields.title: Edit Account
fields.text:
Update Account

  • First Name: Given name.
  • Last Name: Family name.
  • Email: Personal or organization email address. If you change your email an new verification link will be sent to the updated account.
  • Organization: The university or organization that your are affiliated with.
  • Password: Eight character, uncommon, alpha-numeric password. If you change your password, you will need to log in again.

fields.title: Verify Account Resend
fields.text:
Resend Email Verification

You must verify you can access the email account you have specified. If you have not received the a verification link, check the account page and confirm you have the correct email address list. If you have still no received a link, check you spam folder.

fields.title: Verify Account
fields.text:
Verify Email Address

You must verify you have access to the email address you specified. If the link is no longer valid you can send a new one the email address you specified in your account.
